# Deployment Troubleshooting

## Deployment Architecture
- **Frontend**: Netlify at `https://ubiquitous-sherbet-b4f6bf.netlify.app/`
- **Backend**: Railway at `https://backend-production-80f6.up.railway.app/`
- **GitHub**: `https://github.com/BeratGocer/appsamurai-dashboard`

## Deployment Workflow
1. **Code Changes** → Git commit and push
2. **Frontend Build** → `npm run build` (creates dist/)
3. **Netlify Deploy** → `netlify deploy --prod --dir=dist`
4. **Live Testing** → Browser automation with Playwright

## Common Deployment Issues

### Issue: "Frontend değişiminin hemen gelmesi gerekmiyor mu"
**Root Cause**: Changes pushed to Git but not deployed to Netlify
**Solution**: Run `netlify deploy --prod --dir=dist` after Git push

### Issue: "Web sitesinde hala chat kutusunun küçültme tuşunu göremiyorum"
**Root Cause**: Z-index or CSS issues in production
**Solution**: 
- Verify z-index values (z-50 for panel, z-10 for button)
- Check Tailwind classes are compiled correctly
- Test with browser automation

### Issue: "Ayarlara tıkladığımda site boş dönüyor"
**Root Cause**: SettingsPanel conditional rendering logic
**Solution**: Ensure SettingsPanel renders on 'overview' tab

## Live Testing with Playwright
Use browser automation to test deployed features:

```typescript
// Navigate to production site
await page.goto('https://ubiquitous-sherbet-b4f6bf.netlify.app/')

// Test chat functionality
await page.click('[title="Yardımcı"]')
await page.fill('input[placeholder="Mesaj yazın..."]', 'test message')
await page.click('button[title="Gönder"]')

// Test settings access
await page.click('text=Dashboard')
await page.click('text=Ayarlar')
```

## Build Process Verification
Ensure build process includes all changes:

```bash
# Clean build
rm -rf dist/
npm run build

# Verify dist/ contains latest changes
ls -la dist/assets/

# Deploy to production
netlify deploy --prod --dir=dist
```

## Critical Rules
- ✅ Always push to Git before deploying
- ✅ Run `npm run build` before Netlify deploy
- ✅ Test with Playwright after deployment
- ✅ Verify z-index values in production
- ✅ Check conditional rendering logic
- ✅ Monitor Netlify build logs for errors
- ✅ Test all user flows on live site
- ✅ Use browser dev tools to debug CSS issues